title: 820-00165 no green light
message: Hi found corrosion Q7560 and i replaced it. board starts to work fine, but some times not turn on and no greenlight. when apply heat q7560 area green light comes and starts work fine. Where should i start

title: 820-00165 no green light
message:
Resolder U7501 and check traces and surrounding components.
Pay atention to R/C7564.

Do you lose 3V3_S5?
3V42_G3H stable?
Be sure SMC_RESET_L is steady high.
Also check if SMC_PM_G2_EN is maintained.
